WEBVTT

00:00:03.589 --> 00:00:07.270
KALETET MISPAR SHALOSH, Lev Rozov.

00:00:07.791 --> 00:00:14.720
ADON Rozov, ir zent ongekumen keyn Vitebsk. ir zogt, ir hot gezen, s'iz nishto keyn rusishe vidershtand.

00:00:14.473 --> 00:00:16.850
⟨ye⟩. itster ⟨vil ikh aykh zogn⟩,

00:00:17.038 --> 00:00:18.630
itster vil ikh aykh zogn,

00:00:18.630 --> 00:00:20.053
mir zaynen gekumen...

00:00:20.667 --> 00:00:23.664
ikh vil aykh zogn vi azoy mir zaynen gekumen

00:00:23.687 --> 00:00:25.166
in a shtot

00:00:25.290 --> 00:00:30.930
Smolensk. farshraybt, dos iz eyne fun di groyse shtet in Rusland, Smolensk.

00:00:31.045 --> 00:00:36.658
fun Smolensk zaynen mir vayter gegangen. dortn hobn mir shoyn getrofn oyfn veg

00:00:36.985 --> 00:00:42.010
a sakh mentshn. m'hot shoyn ge- ki getribn, di kolkhozn gefirt,

00:00:42.010 --> 00:00:44.859
di mashines aroysgefirt fun Rusland.

00:00:45.085 --> 00:00:50.760
zayn- un ale zaynen gelofn. un mir hobn shoyn geforn oyf a ferd, vayl ikh hob gekhapt a ferd bay eynem

00:00:50.760 --> 00:00:54.530
⟨fun bakante⟩. er hot gevolt opgebn in militer. zog ikh, "ikh bin militer.

00:00:54.530 --> 00:00:57.662
gib mir dem ferd, vel ikh forn. zoln zey mir araynzetsn!"

00:00:57.662 --> 00:00:59.928
⟨ah,⟩ s'iz dokh nit geven keyn ordenung.

00:01:00.019 --> 00:01:04.350
ikh hob genumen un mir zaynen geforn, mir zaynen geforn, mir zaynen geforn oyf Moskeve.

00:01:04.845 --> 00:01:09.720
di veg vos es geyt a hoypt-veg fun Smolensk oyf Moskeve.

00:01:09.720 --> 00:01:12.652
Moskeve zaynen mir gekumen in

00:01:13.418 --> 00:01:17.563
V⟨yaznye⟩, a shtot V⟨yaznye⟩, hinter Moskeve.

00:01:17.653 --> 00:01:20.070
hot men undz gezogt, "stop!"

00:01:21.822 --> 00:01:25.360
ahin, der veg, mer forn tor men nit.

00:01:24.910 --> 00:01:28.245
vi vayt iz fun Smolensk biz,...?

00:01:27.458 --> 00:01:30.790
biz keyn Moskeve? kh'kon, ikh kon es nit zogn afile.

00:01:30.790 --> 00:01:32.640
efsher hundert kilometer.

00:01:32.640 --> 00:01:35.220
s'iz geven di hunderter kilometers!

00:01:35.220 --> 00:01:36.490
s'iz dokh nit geven...

00:01:36.490 --> 00:01:37.960
un mir zaynen gegangen,

00:01:37.960 --> 00:01:41.862
gegangen. dos iz vokhn; dos iz, dos iz nit teg.

00:01:41.641 --> 00:01:44.150
un vos hot ets gegesn? vos...?

00:01:42.848 --> 00:01:47.270
gegesn? iz oyfn veg voltst zikh opshteln, voltstu do epes koyfn, do epes nemen.

00:01:47.270 --> 00:01:48.910
di gantse frage iz geven

00:01:48.910 --> 00:01:50.330
mit arumvashn zikh.

00:01:50.330 --> 00:01:52.663
volt men vu s'iz a taykh nekhtikn,

00:01:52.855 --> 00:01:55.265
bayn tog vashn, bay nakht geyn.

00:01:55.265 --> 00:02:01.020
s'iz nit geven a, antloyfn fun, antloyfn fun Hitlern iz nit geven antloyfn

00:02:01.020 --> 00:02:02.496
fun eynem a mentshn.

00:02:02.496 --> 00:02:07.058
un vu er iz gegangen, hob ikh aykh d- ot itster vel ikh aykh dertseyln eyn zakh:

00:02:07.148 --> 00:02:12.401
vu ikh bin gegangen volt men varfn f- bombes, un di muter volt lign, volt men ir darfn oyfheybn.

00:02:12.401 --> 00:02:14.094
fun shrek aleyn!

00:02:14.252 --> 00:02:17.100
s'volt zayn azetike oyfraysn, shrek aleyn, volt...

00:02:17.100 --> 00:02:20.687
itster gib ikh aykh eyn epizod kedey tsu makhn gikher di zakh.

00:02:20.687 --> 00:02:26.650
mir zaynen gekumen in V⟨yaznye⟩, hot men undz farhaltn un ⟨me⟩ zog⟨t⟩, di yugntlekhe darfn geyn in militer.

00:02:29.254 --> 00:02:32.758
iz hob ikh gelo- tsugefirt di eltern tsu a derfl,

00:02:32.950 --> 00:02:35.829
gelozn zey shteyn mit alts mit an ander,

00:02:36.848 --> 00:02:43.280
un mir zaynen avekgegangen in militer. zogt di klenere... ikh un der bruder... zogt di klenere shvester,

00:02:43.280 --> 00:02:45.499
Manye, "ikh'l mit aykh oykh geyn."

00:02:45.690 --> 00:02:48.226
⟨zog ikh,⟩ zog ikh, "un vi vet men lozn di eltern?"

00:02:48.226 --> 00:02:50.220
mir hobn gelozn di eltern

00:02:50.220 --> 00:02:52.580
ts-, t-, tsvey tekhter

00:02:52.580 --> 00:02:55.390
mit pitslekh tsvey kinder un nokh di...

00:02:53.075 --> 00:02:54.075
UNK

00:02:55.390 --> 00:02:57.500
vi kon i-... zog ikh, "vi vestu geyn?"

00:02:57.500 --> 00:03:01.094
un zi iz geven di bukhhalter; zi iz geven a mentsh oykh mit a kop.

00:03:01.094 --> 00:03:04.989
zog ikh, "ikh veys gornit vi me...", zogt zi, "kum, ikh'l geyn mit aykh."

00:03:05.080 --> 00:03:07.065
⟨geyn,⟩ "kum, kum."

00:03:07.071 --> 00:03:11.148
bin ikh avekgegangen. nor ikh hob gehat a dokument epes vos...

00:03:11.543 --> 00:03:13.055
ikh hob gehat rekht.

00:03:13.382 --> 00:03:16.785
ikh bin avekgegangen. zaynen mir arayng- i-...

00:03:14.884 --> 00:03:18.340
vos far a dok- vos far a dokument hot ir gehat?

00:03:17.955 --> 00:03:24.860
ikh hob gehat a dokument vos ikh bin geven in UNK in der NARODNOE SOBRANIE oysgeklibn. a papirl! a pa-...

00:03:24.860 --> 00:03:30.610
ale dokumentn zaynen geven gornisht: on bilder, on gornisht. s'iz nit geven dokumentn.

00:03:30.610 --> 00:03:31.989
shtikl papir!

00:03:32.181 --> 00:03:33.640
dokument⟨n iz nit⟩ geven,

00:03:33.640 --> 00:03:36.370
nor far zey iz dos geven a DOKUMENT. ir farsht-...

00:03:36.370 --> 00:03:39.448
oder bay hayntikn tog, volt men dos vayzn, lakht men derfun.

00:03:40.146 --> 00:03:43.869
a dokumen-... ikh hob nit gehat keyn eynem mit a bild.

00:03:44.837 --> 00:03:47.770
yeder hot gekent vayzn dokumen-...

00:03:45.597 --> 00:03:48.696
yeder hot gekont nemen mayn dokument un geyn.

00:03:48.887 --> 00:03:51.350
ir farshteyt? do iz nit geven...

00:03:51.350 --> 00:03:54.787
nor dan in t⟨UNK⟩. its- itster vel ikh aykh dertseyln,

00:03:54.878 --> 00:03:59.397
mir zaynen gekumen in V⟨yaznye⟩. me hot shoyn geshtelt di ferd un gekumen bay drit.

00:03:59.397 --> 00:04:02.515
a shtot vos iz gelegn a shpitol.

00:04:02.809 --> 00:04:07.927
ale shrayen: bay dem felt a fus, bay dem felt a hant. m'shrayt, me lyaremt.

00:04:07.927 --> 00:04:11.020
m'hot tsebombirt oyf breklekh.

00:04:11.618 --> 00:04:13.451
kep hot men nor gezen!

00:04:14.672 --> 00:04:16.066
vi ikh zog aykh,

00:04:16.156 --> 00:04:17.972
a kuk geton oyfn shtot:

00:04:18.047 --> 00:04:21.770
sh- shtiklekh fleysh! mir hobn nit gevust vos s'tut zikh.

00:04:21.945 --> 00:04:26.954
shikt men undz, geyen mir dortn: fu⟨l⟩ soldatn, ofitsern,

00:04:26.954 --> 00:04:29.200
groyse mentshn. me shteyt in rey

00:04:29.200 --> 00:04:32.560
farshraybn zikh: "vuhin zol ikh geyn, in velkhn CHAST'?"

00:04:32.560 --> 00:04:36.688
der fregt ahin. ikh bin dokh keyn mol nit geven in militer dortn; ikh veys dokh nit.

00:04:36.745 --> 00:04:38.870
zogt men... a kuk geton oyf undz...

00:04:38.870 --> 00:04:40.614
"ir geyt dortn in a vald."

00:04:40.614 --> 00:04:43.213
arayngegangen in vald, take arayngegangen,

00:04:43.213 --> 00:04:47.180
lign oysgeleygt kupes soldatn,

00:04:47.376 --> 00:04:48.857
un mir ale,

00:04:48.857 --> 00:04:50.575
yugntlekhe, a sakh,

00:04:51.072 --> 00:04:57.714
a gantsn vald f⟨UNK⟩ ikh bin dergangen, arayngegangen in UNK. s'shteyen nokh soldatn mit biksn, me lozt nit. ikh,

00:04:57.940 --> 00:04:59.267
kh'vayz,

00:04:59.681 --> 00:05:01.130
dos dokument?

00:05:00.387 --> 00:05:02.923
dokument. a dokument! a kart-

00:05:02.923 --> 00:05:04.872
ot azoy di greys a kartele,

00:05:04.872 --> 00:05:06.303
vayz ikh zey:

00:05:06.411 --> 00:05:09.600
"VALYAY!" VALYAY iz, gey ikh.

00:05:09.600 --> 00:05:13.460
gekumen ahin, UNK, "ZDRAVSTVUY, TOVARISHCH." "ZDRAVSTVUY."

00:05:13.768 --> 00:05:17.494
nu⟨, iz⟩ freg ikh bay im, "KAK DELA? CHTO..." "DA CHTO TY GOVORISH'?"

00:05:17.494 --> 00:05:22.216
YA GOVORYU, "YA PRISHЁL V ARM⟨IY⟩." "ikh bin gekumen in, in armey zolst mir nemen."

00:05:22.392 --> 00:05:24.343
"KUSHAT' EST' U TEBYA?"

00:05:24.568 --> 00:05:27.720
fregt er bay mir. zog ikh, "OTKUDOVA?

00:05:27.720 --> 00:05:30.806
YA S SOBOY NE... U MENYA NICHEGO NET! VOT TAK."

00:05:30.107 --> 00:05:31.940
vos meynt dos?

00:05:30.964 --> 00:05:33.894
"e-" dos meynt, "esn hostu?"

00:05:35.183 --> 00:05:40.588
zog ikh, "fun vanet? mir zaynen bay drit. UNK dos iz mayn bruder un dos iz di shvester.

00:05:40.588 --> 00:05:41.977
mir hobn gornisht nit."

00:05:42.169 --> 00:05:43.540
zogt er, "VALYAY!"

00:05:43.540 --> 00:05:45.116
zog ikh, "shrayb mir on...

00:05:45.493 --> 00:05:47.309
shrayb mir on a papir.

00:05:47.383 --> 00:05:48.693
⟨vos vel ikh geyn?⟩

00:05:50.590 --> 00:05:53.385
⟨azoy lozt men⟩ dokh undz ergets nit arayn nekhtikn."

00:05:53.982 --> 00:05:58.620
hot er mir epes oykh a shr⟨i⟩b geton dray verter, gegebn a papirl, geshtelt a shtempl,

00:05:58.620 --> 00:06:00.911
gegebn dem papir, un mir zaynen avekgegangen krik.

00:06:01.035 --> 00:06:06.294
mir hobn nit aroys fun dem vald nokh, hot men genumen shitn

00:06:06.520 --> 00:06:08.100
mit bombes.

00:06:08.511 --> 00:06:14.110
iz di, di shvester hot arumgekhapt. mir shrayen ale un me veys nit vos tsu ton.

00:06:14.110 --> 00:06:16.959
arumgenumen, zoln ale, ale glaykh geharget vern.

00:06:17.303 --> 00:06:19.740
a! dos iz ni-... ikh'l aykh zogn:

00:06:19.740 --> 00:06:26.010
iz zaynen mir genumen loyfn. zog ikh, "do shteyn unter vant toyg nit; es vet aynfaln di vant, vet zi undz dershtikn, unter a vant."

00:06:26.010 --> 00:06:28.401
zog ikh, "aynfaln di vant, ⟨⟩, dershtikt zi undz."

00:06:28.407 --> 00:06:30.770
zaynen mir avekgelofn, faln mir arayn vu?

00:06:30.770 --> 00:06:36.470
vu VOENNe, militer shteyt un shist ZENITNe artilerye vos shist oyf di SAMOLЁТn.

00:06:37.013 --> 00:06:40.210
"KUDA VY?!" genumen shrayen oyf undz.

00:06:41.113 --> 00:06:51.150
mir zaynen kam-kam bay nakht aroysgeklibn zikh fun dortn un dergangen bizkl di eltern zaynen. mir hobn gekrokhn a gantse nakht

00:06:51.660 --> 00:06:52.869
bay drit.

00:06:53.449 --> 00:06:55.170
mir kumen vu di el-

00:06:55.356 --> 00:06:57.105
kumen vu di eltern,

00:06:57.415 --> 00:06:58.792
veynen ale.

00:06:59.220 --> 00:07:03.095
der ferd iz fun zey antlofn, lozt ⟨er ze⟩y nit nemen,

00:07:04.435 --> 00:07:05.947
un zey veynen.

00:07:07.219 --> 00:07:10.684
ikh bin gekumen glaykh, gikh gemakht, gikh, alts gikh,

00:07:10.684 --> 00:07:15.788
un s'iz shoyn bald ongehoybn likhtik vern. zog ikh, UNK "zetst zikh!" un ⟨mir zaynen⟩ avekgeforn.

00:07:15.788 --> 00:07:17.962
⟨mir zaynen⟩ avekgeforn, avekgeforn oyf a zayt.

00:07:18.475 --> 00:07:20.522
zey hobn undz gevizn a veg tsu forn.

00:07:20.522 --> 00:07:28.380
gevizn a veg tsu forn. zog ikh nokh tsu di, tsum bruder zog ikh, "mer in militer gey ikh nit. zoln zey mir glaykh oyf an ort shisn, zoln zey ton...

00:07:28.380 --> 00:07:29.927
ikh gey ergets nit mer!

00:07:30.388 --> 00:07:31.549
mir veln forn."

00:07:31.549 --> 00:07:37.180
forn, hot men undz avekgeshikt... ⟨kurts tsu⟩ makhn, zaynen mir durkhgeforn a shtot KALUGA.

00:07:37.628 --> 00:07:39.730
farshraybt a shtot KALUGA.

00:07:39.822 --> 00:07:42.685
KALUGA iz shoyn gekumen di makht.

00:07:42.825 --> 00:07:48.700
dos iz shoyn geven vayt ahin, veys ikh nit tsi der daytsh iz dortn geven tsi nit, kon ikh afile nit, i- veys ikh afile nit.

00:07:48.917 --> 00:07:53.706
nor dos iz shoyn in der zayt fun Moskve; Moskve iz geli⟨UNK⟩n shoyn on a zayt.

00:07:53.706 --> 00:07:55.459
dos iz an ander veg.

00:07:55.650 --> 00:08:00.389
⟨dortn⟩ bin ikh, ⟨dortn bin ikh⟩ gekumen, hot UNK hot men genumen,

00:08:00.389 --> 00:08:08.030
opgenumen bay undz di ferd, un m'hot undz gegebn alts... alts shraybt men ⟨oder⟩ a papirl ⟨UBEDIT'⟩. opgenumen, avekgegebn.

00:08:08.030 --> 00:08:09.966
di ferd hot di militer alts tsugenumen,

00:08:09.966 --> 00:08:11.999
bay alemen! s'iz geven a sakh...

00:08:11.999 --> 00:08:18.080
s'iz geven bakonte, ho⟨bn⟩ mir keyn⟨e⟩ nit derkont. ⟨ikh bin geven a farvaks- aza⟩ bord. ⟨az⟩

00:08:18.080 --> 00:08:20.480
mi- mir dreyen zikh um ts- tsvey monat,

00:08:20.480 --> 00:08:23.775
nit keyn vashn... ir veyst dokh shoyn vi me zet oys!

00:08:23.882 --> 00:08:25.520
un azoy far⟨havet⟩.

00:08:25.520 --> 00:08:29.950
un dortn hob ikh gefunen dem mentshn vos s'iz mayn, pekl

00:08:29.950 --> 00:08:32.077
mitn, mit dem mantl.

00:08:31.965 --> 00:08:35.560
hot ir, im dort getrofn. mit...

00:08:32.573 --> 00:08:36.340
oykh getrofn dortn. s'iz nit, s'iz nit geven azoy...

00:08:36.340 --> 00:08:38.200
vayle m'hot geyogt alemen

00:08:38.200 --> 00:08:42.700
in eyn ort. vu er iz nit geforn, s'iz nit geven vuhin tsu forn.

00:08:43.322 --> 00:08:45.470
s'iz nit geven vuhin tsu forn!

00:08:45.470 --> 00:08:47.546
der vos UNK in eyn ort.

00:08:47.546 --> 00:08:50.673
dortn zaynen mir gezesn bay nakht,

00:08:51.220 --> 00:08:54.960
a gantse nakht, un m'hot ongehoybn undz oykh bombirn.

00:08:55.017 --> 00:09:00.480
ongehoybn bombirn, iz vu es treft, treft, oder vemen treft nit, treft nit. mir veysn dokh nit;

00:09:00.480 --> 00:09:01.560
s'iz bay nakht.

00:09:01.560 --> 00:09:03.197
me shrayt, me veynt.

00:09:03.197 --> 00:09:06.215
m'hot tsugefirt a eshelo- a ban

00:09:06.323 --> 00:09:08.910
vu me firt fabrikes.

00:09:09.428 --> 00:09:12.409
a platf- groyse, glate azetike...

00:09:12.583 --> 00:09:14.821
"VALYAYTE! geyt, zetst zikh ale."

00:09:15.334 --> 00:09:16.948
oyf azetike...

00:09:17.376 --> 00:09:21.160
on, nit a dakh, shoyn nito afile... az du voltst zikh gebn a shtup, falstu arop;

00:09:21.160 --> 00:09:23.124
nito far vos ontsuhaltn zikh.

00:09:22.810 --> 00:09:25.000
n- on a zaytn?

00:09:24.362 --> 00:09:28.119
on zaytn, on gornisht nit; a glat, vos me firt ayzn.

00:09:28.311 --> 00:09:32.405
mir hobn zikh ale tsezetst dortn, aroyfgekrokhn un tsezetst, iz...

00:09:32.698 --> 00:09:35.797
froyen hobn geshrien. zbenk! zbenk!

00:09:35.871 --> 00:09:39.138
meshuge gevorn, un klapt zikh in kop un klapt zikh.

00:09:39.364 --> 00:09:41.610
yunge mentshn, ⟨hert⟩.

00:09:41.610 --> 00:09:45.550
mentshn hobn nit gekont kukn oyf dem.

00:09:47.059 --> 00:09:48.448
mir hobn getrofn,

00:09:48.448 --> 00:09:51.970
iz der, getrofn dem rov's a zun.,

00:09:51.970 --> 00:09:53.800
er iz oykh geforn mit der vayb.

00:09:53.800 --> 00:09:55.778
itst-... s'iz nit geven tsu reydn.

00:09:55.935 --> 00:09:59.530
yederer iz geven f- yeder iz geven far zikh.

00:09:59.530 --> 00:10:03.280
eyner tsum tsveytn helfn hot men nit getrakht afile.

00:10:03.280 --> 00:10:05.120
er hot nit getra-... az,

00:10:05.120 --> 00:10:07.520
az s'iz geven aza lage: nit esn,

00:10:07.520 --> 00:10:10.000
nit trinken. vu du khapst, gistu an es,

00:10:10.000 --> 00:10:11.876
oder s'iz dokh nit keyn lebn.

00:10:12.490 --> 00:10:18.829
un mir zaynen geforn, un m'hot undz opgefirt, opgefirt. vuhin firt men undz?

00:10:19.172 --> 00:10:23.362
ikh veys ⟨dokh nit⟩ vuhin me firt. a-, ikh kon aykh zogn vuhin me firt. me firt,

00:10:23.362 --> 00:10:28.619
⟨m'iz aro-⟩ un me shtelt op, darf ⟨me⟩n nokh epes, aropgeyn., es iz dokh nit azoy...

00:10:28.619 --> 00:10:31.451
ersht me hot undz ongehoybn bombirn,

00:10:32.149 --> 00:10:33.960
oyfn veg.

00:10:34.258 --> 00:10:36.570
der ban hot zikh avekgeshtelt

00:10:37.127 --> 00:10:43.320
un m'hot bombirt, zaynen mir ale tselofn. der bruder hot gekhapt beyde kinder, arayngelofn in a vald nit vayt.

00:10:44.113 --> 00:10:47.532
dos hot gedoyert efsher tsvey, dray sho.

00:10:47.708 --> 00:10:51.836
s'iz nokh geven likhtik. bizn s'iz gevorn nakht, nito der bruder mit di kinder.

00:10:52.956 --> 00:10:54.604
nisht tsurikgekumen?

00:10:54.475 --> 00:10:56.699
nito der bruder mit di kinder.

00:10:56.699 --> 00:11:01.880
ongehoybn shrayen UNK shrayen, "Gedalye! Gedalye! ⟨le-⟩ shray!"

00:11:01.880 --> 00:11:09.160
bizn es, fun vaytn hot er undz derzen. er iz gekumen tsu loyfn. er iz farkrokhn in vald, hot er nit gevust vi azoy aroystsukrikhn.

00:11:06.743 --> 00:11:09.120
nisht gevust vi aroys.

00:11:10.692 --> 00:11:15.023
⟨m'iz⟩ gekumen mit di kinder, iz shoyn, di khalesht, UNK. ikh'l aykh zogn, s'iz dokh,

00:11:15.079 --> 00:11:21.830
dos kon men nit derts-... az ikh zol dos veln rikhtik zitsn, darf men zitsn tsvey teg un trakhtn.

00:11:22.217 --> 00:11:23.898
ot dos iz geven.

00:11:24.057 --> 00:11:29.788
⟨hot er⟩ gekumen, mir hobn zikh avekgezetst... itster vil ikh aykh endikn... m'hot undz gebrakht biz KUYBYSHEV.

00:11:30.469 --> 00:11:32.430
KUYBYSHEV, dos iz shoyn

00:11:32.430 --> 00:11:35.000
di letste shtot fun Rusland,

00:11:35.886 --> 00:11:38.478
vos dortn iz der daytsh take nit geven.

00:11:38.873 --> 00:11:43.010
dortn hot men undz geheysn arop, alemen,

00:11:43.010 --> 00:11:46.851
un m'hot undz oyfn gas... s'iz shoyn geven ful mentshn!

00:11:46.851 --> 00:11:49.644
m'iz nokh yedern gegangen un geshribn

00:11:49.644 --> 00:11:52.450
fun vanet, vuhin,

00:11:52.450 --> 00:11:55.000
vuhin vilstu, vos vilstu...

00:11:55.000 --> 00:11:56.856
dortn hot zikh gerufn

00:11:56.980 --> 00:12:00.264
der UNK der punkt vos shikt fanander di mentshn.

00:12:00.456 --> 00:12:03.780
iz shoyn, az eyner volt shoyn veln... dos iz geven der,

00:12:03.780 --> 00:12:06.190
dos hot zikh gerufn der punkt KINEL'.

00:12:06.190 --> 00:12:10.210
⟨e-⟩ dortn hot men gekont gefinen mentshn, vayl dortn iz shoyn geven

00:12:10.210 --> 00:12:12.480
geshribn pleytim. s'iz nit geven mir,

00:12:12.480 --> 00:12:14.250
eyn mishpokhe. pleytim!

00:12:14.250 --> 00:12:16.770
⟨iz dokh⟩ geven fun, Rusland iz dokh groys.

00:12:16.770 --> 00:12:20.548
shoyn rusishe, vos shoyn, fun umetum zaynen geven dortn.

00:12:20.723 --> 00:12:22.539
⟨m'hot⟩ farshribn undz.

00:12:23.170 --> 00:12:24.846
der bruder, zogt er,

00:12:24.846 --> 00:12:27.855
"vuhin zoln mir betn zikh? ⟨ikh⟩ veys nit vuhin tsu betn zikh."

00:12:27.861 --> 00:12:31.922
zogn zey, zogn mir azoy: "ale nakete? ale nakete.

00:12:32.147 --> 00:12:34.267
vu s'iz kalt torn mir nit forn."

00:12:34.358 --> 00:12:37.100
un dos iz dokh vinter, shoyn erev vinter.

00:12:36.527 --> 00:12:38.740
ets hots gornisht UNK...

00:12:37.500 --> 00:12:40.224
UNK ⟨nito vos⟩ afile... keyner nit!

00:12:40.613 --> 00:12:42.250
velkhe mo- v-...

00:12:40.669 --> 00:12:43.700
tomer der foter hot nor gehalt dem tales un tfiln,

00:12:43.700 --> 00:12:46.265
hot er gehalt unter orem un dos iz es.

00:12:46.350 --> 00:12:49.570
di tales un tfiln hot er mitgenumen ven er iz antlofn.

00:12:47.790 --> 00:12:52.810
mitgenumen di ga- ⟨n-⟩ zet ir, alts hot er, dem eygenem mantl gevorfn;

00:12:52.810 --> 00:12:55.242
dem tales un tfiln hot er nit gevorfn.

00:12:56.987 --> 00:12:58.440
ir farshteyt?

00:12:58.945 --> 00:13:03.090
in velkhe monat zent ir shoyn geven? dos iz shoyn geven vinter?

00:13:00.902 --> 00:13:05.587
o, dos iz shoyn geven, ikh, ikh, ikh gedenk nit genoy, nor s'iz geven av- a-

00:13:05.593 --> 00:13:08.920
avgust, september. ⟨es iz⟩ shoyn a por monat UNK...

00:13:07.635 --> 00:13:10.170
s'iz shoyn ongehoybn tsu vern kalt.

00:13:09.728 --> 00:13:13.057
s'hot shoyn ongehoybn geyn tsum vinter, hot ongehoybn geyn.

00:13:13.057 --> 00:13:14.986
hob⟨n mir⟩ gezogt dem bruder...

00:13:15.145 --> 00:13:20.040
zog ikh, "gey bet, d- du gey bet..." ikh bin avekgegangen in restoran ⟨efsher⟩...

00:13:20.646 --> 00:13:22.870
hob ikh shoyn oysgetrunken a bisl.

00:13:22.870 --> 00:13:26.456
ikh'l ay-... zog ikh, "du gey bet, vuhin du vilst, bet."

00:13:26.456 --> 00:13:29.030
⟨iz⟩ der bruder avekgegangen, zogt er, "Tashkent."

00:13:30.923 --> 00:13:33.520
Tashkent, Tashkent. firt men undz.

00:13:33.520 --> 00:13:36.691
hot men bald gebrakht.... d⟨UNK⟩ gedoyert nokh efsher a tog...

00:13:36.691 --> 00:13:38.646
m'hot gebrakht vagones,

00:13:39.057 --> 00:13:43.643
oykh TOVARNe vagones, in der heykh opgetsamt, tseleygt mit shtroy

00:13:43.643 --> 00:13:49.160
⟨oybn, un⟩ gezogt, "gey!" vifl mentshn? mistome arayngegangen tsvantsik mentshn, finf un tsvantsik.

00:13:49.160 --> 00:13:50.990
dos ge⟨UNK⟩ tsvey mishpo- eyn,

00:13:50.990 --> 00:13:53.170
nokh eyne tsu undz iz geven a mishpokhe.

00:13:53.170 --> 00:13:55.240
a mishpokhe, vos far a mishpokhe?

00:13:55.240 --> 00:14:00.280
mentshn in di fertsiker yorn, a man un vayb, mit a por kinder, mit an alte mame,

00:14:00.280 --> 00:14:02.231
hobn zey gehat, oykh geven dortn.

00:14:02.231 --> 00:14:06.078
un zaynen mir shoyn gehat, bay undz iz geven a dokter a rusisher, un s'iz geven bay mir

00:14:06.078 --> 00:14:09.290
fun, fun Letland eyne,

00:14:09.290 --> 00:14:11.774
un s'iz geven d- alts fun di...

00:14:11.774 --> 00:14:15.630
vu ir volt khapn. mer fun alemen iz geven yugntlekhe,

00:14:16.300 --> 00:14:17.930
nor yugntlekhe.

00:14:16.317 --> 00:14:19.640
di yunge mentshn hobn gekent antloyfn.

00:14:17.930 --> 00:14:21.100
az ikh bin shoyn geven bay zey oykh an elterer;

00:14:21.100 --> 00:14:23.249
⟨kh'bin⟩ shoyn geven a por un draysik yor.

00:14:21.615 --> 00:14:23.710
vi alt zent ir geven?

00:14:23.249 --> 00:14:24.275
vos?

00:14:23.710 --> 00:14:25.946
vi alt zent ir geven?

00:14:25.378 --> 00:14:29.540
ikh bin dan geven, in yene yorn bin ikh shoyn geven tsvey, dray un draysik yor.

00:14:30.576 --> 00:14:32.650
shoyn geven an e- geven a e-

00:14:32.650 --> 00:14:35.143
vi haynt iz dos shoyn a, a elterer.

00:14:35.320 --> 00:14:38.300
ikh hob shoyn durkhgemakht a lebn. ikh hob shoyn, ikh bin dokh, shoyn, shoyn...

00:14:38.300 --> 00:14:43.330
gevezn azoy. zaynen mir avekgeforn, nor dos, kurts darf men makhn, vayl dos iz nokh ⟨ot do⟩...

00:14:43.330 --> 00:14:44.756
avekgeforn ahin.

00:14:44.756 --> 00:14:50.890
zaynen mir, hot men undz avekgeshikt, tsugeforn bizn Tashkent. kh'hob Rusland gezen fun ale zaytn.

00:14:50.890 --> 00:14:54.510
tsugeforn bizn Tashkent, bin ikh mitn foter aropgekrokhn.

00:14:54.510 --> 00:14:58.550
un dortn epes hot men gearbet, ikh ⟨veys⟩ vos, zog ikh, "me kon bay aykh arbetn?"

00:14:58.550 --> 00:15:00.788
zogn zey, "POZHALUYSTA, POZHALUYSTA!"

00:15:00.788 --> 00:15:04.719
iz zog ikh, "⟨gu- gut, me zol⟩ do aropzetsn UNK ⟨nemen⟩ arbetn."

00:15:04.719 --> 00:15:07.543
zogt, ⟨es iz g-⟩ untergegangen ⟨a⟩ N.K.V.D.:

00:15:08.815 --> 00:15:11.627
fun di vagones zol keyner nit aroys,

00:15:12.375 --> 00:15:14.006
UNK do iz nito keyn ort.

00:15:14.772 --> 00:15:17.078
un m'hot undz avekgefirt vayter.

00:15:17.387 --> 00:15:20.114
vayter, gebrakht in a shtot LOYISH...

00:15:20.425 --> 00:15:22.500
ikh gedenk ⟨nit⟩, darf dokh gedenken ale

00:15:22.500 --> 00:15:23.855
shtet mit nemen...

00:15:23.855 --> 00:15:28.300
dos iz geven UZBEKISTAN. UZBEKISTAN.

00:15:28.930 --> 00:15:31.168
oto dos iz UZBEKISTAN.

00:15:31.410 --> 00:15:35.774
in LOYISH, dortn hot men shoyn undz aropgelozn

00:15:36.253 --> 00:15:39.820
un gezogt, "z- farnemt zikh an ort."

00:15:41.502 --> 00:15:47.270
⟨es iz do?⟩ do zitsn, do zitsn d⟨UNK⟩ farnumen a vinkl oyfn gas.

00:15:47.270 --> 00:15:49.328
nito, keyn shtub iz nito,

00:15:49.328 --> 00:15:53.390
n⟨or⟩ oyfn gas farnumen an ort. dortn iz der klimat varem,

00:15:53.390 --> 00:15:54.945
pakhozhe oyf Erets-Yisroel.

00:15:55.575 --> 00:15:56.919
s'iz mitl-Azye.

00:15:57.600 --> 00:16:00.243
nu, dortn hobn mir zikh opgeshtelt.

00:16:00.486 --> 00:16:05.680
bay undz iz shoyn geven a STOLOVe, m'hot UNK farshraybn. nor vos? es iz shoyn geven a SHUK.

00:16:05.903 --> 00:16:09.760
avekgegangen, hot men gekoyft, di ershte zakh hot men alemen tsekoyft

00:16:09.760 --> 00:16:13.069
dekes, az me zol zikh hobn oyf vos tsu leygn oyf der erd.

00:16:12.660 --> 00:16:14.604
e- ets hots gehat gelt?

00:16:14.340 --> 00:16:16.140
⟨m-⟩ ikh hob gehat ⟨gelt⟩.

00:16:14.998 --> 00:16:16.612
ir hot gehat.

00:16:16.251 --> 00:16:17.640
⟨ikh hob gehat gelt⟩.

00:16:18.036 --> 00:16:22.680
kh'hob gehat, ikh hob gehat, ikh hob gekont hobn mer gelt; ikh hob di froy ibergelozt gelt.

00:16:22.778 --> 00:16:24.760
ikh hob gehat gelt.

00:16:23.942 --> 00:16:28.270
ir hot gehat di gantse tsayt, di por khadoshim vos ir zent gelofn,

00:16:28.009 --> 00:16:29.740
hob ikh gefi-...

00:16:28.270 --> 00:16:31.190
hot ir gehat kontakt mit,

00:16:30.912 --> 00:16:32.225
mit keynem nit!

00:16:31.190 --> 00:16:33.220
mit di froy? ir ho-...

00:16:32.225 --> 00:16:33.706
mit vemen?

00:16:33.220 --> 00:16:35.870
ir hot nisht gevust vos s'tut zikh dort?

00:16:34.422 --> 00:16:36.570
nit ikh veys vos s'tut z-...

00:16:36.570 --> 00:16:41.503
tsvey, ⟨d-⟩... hert azoy: dray kilometer nokh mir, veys ikh nit vos s'tut zikh.

00:16:42.184 --> 00:16:45.198
far vos? di militer veys oykh nit vos s'tut zikh.

00:16:45.272 --> 00:16:47.500
do loyft militer un dortn militer,

00:16:47.500 --> 00:16:51.610
du bist do in vald, dortn in vald. fun vemen? telefon? radyo?

00:16:51.610 --> 00:16:54.770
UNK gornisht nit gevust! ⟨m'hot⟩ afile ⟨eyn⟩ radyo nit gehat.

00:16:55.026 --> 00:16:58.540
di gantse tsayt hobn mir keyn kontakt nit gehat.

00:16:58.254 --> 00:17:00.066
UND ir hot zikh, ir hot ge-

00:17:00.291 --> 00:17:02.790
ir hot moyre gehat? ir hot ge⟨UNK⟩...

00:17:01.573 --> 00:17:03.370
mir hobn, nit fun moyre!

00:17:03.370 --> 00:17:06.310
⟨az⟩ s'iz nit geven mit vemen tsu hobn kontakt; m'hot di gantse tsayt,

00:17:06.310 --> 00:17:08.410
 gemuzt, gemuzt loyfn,

00:17:06.684 --> 00:17:07.684
gelofn.

00:17:08.410 --> 00:17:10.940
vayle vu du loyfst, der daytsh shlogt,

00:17:10.940 --> 00:17:15.180
shlogt alemen un, un der daytsh iz hinter dir. der foter iz aropgegangen in a dorf,

00:17:15.180 --> 00:17:17.900
zogt eyne tsu im oyf rusish, epes a froy,

00:17:17.900 --> 00:17:20.490
"KUDA VY? NEMTSY ZDES' KHODYAT!"

00:17:21.250 --> 00:17:25.340
mir hobn nit gevust vu der daytsh iz, m- nit mir hobn gevust vu mir zaynen.

00:17:25.340 --> 00:17:28.010
az mir hobn nit gevust vu mir zaynen!

00:17:28.945 --> 00:17:31.940
az ikh volt zayn, volt ikh zogn vu ikh bin; ikh veys nit.

00:17:31.940 --> 00:17:35.334
ikh bin oyf mayn lebn dortn nit getrakht tsu zayn un nit geven.

00:17:36.927 --> 00:17:38.170
s'iz nit azoy.

00:17:38.170 --> 00:17:40.280
un do hitstu ⟨az s'⟩zol, der,

00:17:40.280 --> 00:17:43.250
me geyt op finf trit, kon men shoyn im nit gefinen,

00:17:43.250 --> 00:17:44.801
vayl s'iz ful mentshn.

00:17:45.718 --> 00:17:48.513
darf men zikh haltn eyner tsu di andere.

00:17:48.925 --> 00:17:50.240
s'iz nit geven,

00:17:50.240 --> 00:17:54.724
di lage fun dem antloyfn iz geven punkt vi bay Hitlern zayn.

00:17:54.983 --> 00:17:58.990
di zelbe zakh! az der lebn iz bay zey nit geven keyn lebn bikhlal.

00:17:58.990 --> 00:18:01.520
vegn zikh, vegn lebn host nit getrakht.

00:18:02.728 --> 00:18:03.813
ir farshteyt?

00:18:03.813 --> 00:18:07.670
ot dos, oto dos iz geven undzer antloyfn.

00:18:07.670 --> 00:18:10.125
derfar zog ikh, der antloyfn

00:18:10.125 --> 00:18:11.730
un der rateven zikh

00:18:11.730 --> 00:18:15.540
iz geven di zelbe zakh vi antloyfn fun Hitlern,

00:18:15.540 --> 00:18:16.800
tsu zayn bay Hitlern.

00:18:16.800 --> 00:18:21.090
vemen s'hot opgegoltn, der ⟨iz⟩ in geto geblibn; vemen s'hot opgegoltn, iz der in,

00:18:21.090 --> 00:18:24.190
in lager geblibn. dos iz a, dos iz

00:18:24.190 --> 00:18:27.280
a UNK a GORAL fun lebn.

00:18:27.636 --> 00:18:29.030
a GORAL fun lebn!

00:18:29.779 --> 00:18:31.810
opgegoltn, opgegoltn.

00:18:32.395 --> 00:18:34.400
ot iz der foter mit di muter,

00:18:34.400 --> 00:18:41.166
iz mir UNK vu zey hobn gelebt in LOYISH... mir zaynen dortn nit geven lang, vayle di, undz hot men dokh tsugenumen in militer glaykh...

00:18:41.166 --> 00:18:42.830
iz vu zey zaynen gelegn,

00:18:42.830 --> 00:18:49.040
bin ikh, ⟨i-⟩ bin ikh gezen, az du geyst farbay, eyner shloft un vayter shloft, un UNK shloft. toyte mentshn!

00:18:49.118 --> 00:18:50.242
fun hunger.

00:18:52.527 --> 00:18:56.180
nor vos? zey hot oysgehaltn di klenere tokhter,

00:18:56.180 --> 00:18:59.600
⟨vayl di⟩ klenere tokhter iz gekumen a-... di klenere shvester...

00:18:59.600 --> 00:19:01.240
iz gekumen ahin,

00:19:01.240 --> 00:19:03.720
hot zi ongekumen far a bukhhalter

00:19:03.720 --> 00:19:06.880
in an ort vu s'iz esn-zakhn geven.

00:19:07.275 --> 00:19:09.030
hot zi oykh, hot men ir...

00:19:07.309 --> 00:19:09.035
hot zi gekent shikn.

00:19:09.030 --> 00:19:09.786
vos?

00:19:09.460 --> 00:19:11.370
hot zi gekent shikn.

00:19:09.786 --> 00:19:12.380
hot zi zey, hot zi gehaltn zey.

00:19:12.380 --> 00:19:17.280
iz vil ikh aykh zogn, zi hot zey gemakht a kartl oyf finf h- fir hundert gram esn,

00:19:17.280 --> 00:19:20.671
hot men ir avekgeshikt in a lager oyf dray khadoshim.

00:19:20.671 --> 00:19:23.830
mir hobn geshribn tsu KALININen, un mir hobn geshribn...

00:19:23.830 --> 00:19:25.740
un undz iz ongekumen glaykh a briv.

00:19:25.740 --> 00:19:30.310
nor zet, ⟨ot⟩ dortn, az mir zaynen geven ⟨ge⟩mobilizirt, iz mit zey hobn mir gehat

00:19:30.310 --> 00:19:32.160
a, a kontakt,

00:19:32.160 --> 00:19:36.080
vayl dortn vu mir zaynen geven iz oykh der daytsh nit geven; er hot nor gebombirt,

00:19:36.080 --> 00:19:37.970
oder zayn dortn iz er nit geven,

00:19:37.970 --> 00:19:40.102
iz hobn mir gehat a kontakt mit zey.

00:19:40.102 --> 00:19:42.400
hot zi opgeven in a lager,

00:19:42.696 --> 00:19:45.090
biz mir hobn geshribn tsu KALININen...

00:19:43.160 --> 00:19:47.536
v- vayl zi hot, vayl zi hot ge- gemakht a karte far esn?

00:19:47.404 --> 00:19:52.612
zi hot gemakht a kartl oyf esn far di mame mitn tatn, fir hundert gram broyt a tog.

00:19:53.395 --> 00:19:56.360
iz shoyn, oto do volt geven finf un tsvantsik yor turme,

00:19:56.360 --> 00:19:58.420
nor ir hot men gegebn lager, iz zi opgeven...

00:19:58.420 --> 00:20:00.656
nokh dem, az mir hobn geshribn KALININen

00:20:00.656 --> 00:20:06.720
az dray brider zaynen mir oyf milkhome. dray! eyner iz dortn, veysn mir nit vos s'tut zikh fun im,

00:20:06.720 --> 00:20:10.070
un der ferter iz der shvoger, un di kinder zaynen dortn.

00:20:10.070 --> 00:20:12.288
bay di shvester iz di kind geshtorbn.

00:20:12.902 --> 00:20:15.393
a kind iz geshtorbn in Rusland?

00:20:16.159 --> 00:20:18.420
nor eyn kind hot men gebrakht krik;

00:20:18.505 --> 00:20:20.520
di andere hot men nit gebrakht krik.

00:20:20.520 --> 00:20:21.620
ot dos iz geven,

00:20:21.620 --> 00:20:23.513
oto dos iz geven der lebn

00:20:23.513 --> 00:20:28.650
mitn antloyfn. zey zaynen geven dortn; undz hot men gemobilizirt, avekgeshikt oyf arbet.

00:20:28.650 --> 00:20:33.250
iz ikh vil aykh zogn, di ershte tsaytn hobn mir a yor tsayt shv- zeyer shver,

00:20:33.250 --> 00:20:35.224
dortn a mol geven in a lager, shver,

00:20:35.224 --> 00:20:42.530
nor, zey hobn gehat mit undz, a geshprekh, hot men mir aroysgenumen mit dem bruder. m'hot undz aroysgenumen fun ⟨d-⟩...

00:20:35.650 --> 00:20:37.190
vu ze-...

00:20:41.083 --> 00:20:44.900
in velekhn lager zent ir geven? vu hot men aykh geshikt?

00:20:44.087 --> 00:20:50.645
BERENDEEVO hot zikh geheysn, a torf, ⟨a t-⟩ dortn iz torf-arbet, oysarbetung. s'iz geven UNK

00:20:50.719 --> 00:20:54.960
tsvey hundert kilometer, tsvey hundert fertsik, ⟨tsva-,⟩ fertsik kilometer fun Moskeve.

00:20:54.960 --> 00:20:56.880
unter Moskve iz dos geven.

00:20:56.828 --> 00:20:59.809
vi lang zent ir geven in dem lager?

00:20:58.752 --> 00:21:01.733
dortn shoyn bizn ende, biz ende krig.

00:21:02.633 --> 00:21:05.460
biz ende... vayl dortn hot zikh ongerufn

00:21:02.640 --> 00:21:04.500
un ir hot gehat f-...

00:21:05.460 --> 00:21:07.810
VOENNOSLUZHASHCHIY. ir veyst dokh vos...

00:21:07.810 --> 00:21:11.160
a militerisher, er, er dint in militer, alts eyns

00:21:11.160 --> 00:21:12.920
UNK mir hobn ge- ikh hob gearbet

00:21:12.920 --> 00:21:15.010
oyf di tekhnishe SNABZHENIE,

00:21:15.010 --> 00:21:16.960
di tekhnishe... ikh volt tsushteln,

00:21:16.960 --> 00:21:19.510
ikh volt darfn tsushteln neft,

00:21:19.510 --> 00:21:22.830
di, tsu di mashines, t⟨ekh-⟩ teyln, oto di zakhn.

00:21:22.830 --> 00:21:26.050
bin ikh umgeforn iber di fabrikn azh in Ural un umetum.

00:21:26.050 --> 00:21:28.310
ikh hob shoyn gehat a farantvortlekhe arbet,

00:21:28.310 --> 00:21:32.080
durkhgeforn in Moskve makhn az me zol gebn vu, vos tsu krign,

00:21:32.080 --> 00:21:34.976
oto di... ikh hob shoyn gehat an arbet vos ikh hob gearbet.

00:21:33.970 --> 00:21:38.216
hot ir gekent hobn kontakt oykh mit di eltern demolts?

00:21:37.598 --> 00:21:41.220
iz hert ir, zikher, mir hobn gehat kontakt!

00:21:41.220 --> 00:21:46.164
hobn zey geshribn az s'iz, me shtarbt fun hunger. vifl gelt mir hobn zey geshikt,

00:21:46.221 --> 00:21:50.340
kon men lebn a tog; s'iz der broyt zeyer tayer un s'iz nito vos tsu krign,

00:21:50.340 --> 00:21:53.213
un dortn iz geven di krankeyt dizenterye.

00:21:53.213 --> 00:21:55.150
ir veyst vos dos iz?

00:21:54.827 --> 00:21:57.040
iz ver hot gehat dizenterye?

00:21:56.413 --> 00:21:59.815
dizenterye hot der foter ongehoybn hobn, vayle

00:21:59.957 --> 00:22:03.290
er volt esn fun di beymer nor⟨,⟩ zakh,

00:22:03.290 --> 00:22:07.426
⟨, vos⟩ volt aropfaln fun di beymer, un on broyt, on gornisht, hot im...

00:22:07.888 --> 00:22:13.620
iz er gevorn geshvoln. di muter hot gehat MALYARIYA... iz geven a MALYAR⟨IYNOE BOLOTO⟩... beyde gelegn kranke.

00:22:13.677 --> 00:22:17.390
hob ikh in fir un fertsiktn yor... dos endik ikh shoyn bald...

00:22:17.390 --> 00:22:21.030
in fir un fertsiktn yor ongehoybn arbetn mitn bruder,

00:22:21.030 --> 00:22:24.673
hobn mir ongehoybn arbetn az me zol mir gebn dokumentn brengen mentshn.

00:22:24.932 --> 00:22:28.610
un fun dortn hot men undz gefirt mentshn oyf der arbet;

00:22:28.610 --> 00:22:30.400
me volt mobilizirn mentshn.

00:22:30.400 --> 00:22:32.621
ikh hob nit geshribn velkhe mentshn.

00:22:32.931 --> 00:22:35.580
hot men mir gegebn aza dokument,

00:22:35.580 --> 00:22:38.130
⟨a min⟩ dokument, un m'hot mir gegebn a monat.

00:22:38.398 --> 00:22:40.133
in a monat tsayt

00:22:40.133 --> 00:22:43.810
bin ikh avekgeforn ahin, bin ikh geforn mistome tsen teg

00:22:43.810 --> 00:22:45.320
nor ahingeforn,

00:22:45.320 --> 00:22:48.115
un krik zenen mir geforn mer vi tsvey vokhn.

00:22:48.115 --> 00:22:51.420
kh'bin gekumen in KUYBYSHEV, ⟨K-⟩ durkh KUYBYSHEV...

00:22:51.420 --> 00:22:53.600
dos iz, dos iz zeyer vayt. durkh

00:22:53.600 --> 00:22:56.600
Kazakhstaner STEPes darf men forn. dos iz

00:22:56.600 --> 00:22:59.260
a, a, a, a, fun Rusland dos iz zeyer a,

00:22:59.290 --> 00:23:02.189
a sakonedike. s'iz nito keyn vaser.

00:23:02.189 --> 00:23:05.630
mir zaynen dortn gelofn oykh on vaser. dos iz a, zeyer a...

00:23:05.630 --> 00:23:08.470
kh'vil aykh nit dertseyln alts, nor ikh dertseyl aykh kurts...

00:23:08.520 --> 00:23:10.100
az ikh bin geforn

00:23:10.100 --> 00:23:14.180
un ikh hob zey, ikh bin gekumen ahin, iz geven a poylisher dokter, Pikman.

00:23:14.180 --> 00:23:15.393
zogt er tsu mir...

00:23:15.393 --> 00:23:17.560
Pikman, a dokter a yidisher;

00:23:17.560 --> 00:23:19.360
nokh fun di poyln iz er antlofn...

00:23:19.360 --> 00:23:21.040
do iz shoyn gevorn di poylishe,

00:23:21.040 --> 00:23:24.080
di poylishe brigade iz gevorn vos ⟨s'iz⟩ gevorn.

00:23:24.080 --> 00:23:27.350
iz di poylishe brigade gevorn, hot men undz shoyn gevolt nemen,

00:23:27.350 --> 00:23:29.370
ot di poylishe; ikh bin dokh geven in poylishn militer,

00:23:29.370 --> 00:23:33.020
nor di fabrik hot shoyn undz nit opgelozt, vayle zi hot undz gegebn

00:23:33.020 --> 00:23:35.740
BRON'. dos heyst, zi hot undz farhaltn oyf arbet.

00:23:35.740 --> 00:23:37.930
zi hot UNK mir hobn gehat dortn mit di ⟨fa-⟩

00:23:37.930 --> 00:23:40.358
mit di, mit di khevre, hobn mir zey gegebn

00:23:40.380 --> 00:23:42.440
in hant dos, yents.

00:23:42.440 --> 00:23:46.660
un lebn hot men gedarft, un farn lebn hot men gedarft trakhtn aleyn.

00:23:47.097 --> 00:23:49.943
dos hot men gedarft trakhtn aleyn vegn lebn.

00:23:49.999 --> 00:23:53.995
bin ikh avekgeforn un ikh hob di eltern gebrakht ahin,

00:23:53.995 --> 00:23:55.511
di gantse mishpokhe.

00:23:56.310 --> 00:23:59.021
zaynen zey dortn geven a gantsn yor.

00:23:59.601 --> 00:24:02.070
fun fir un fertsik...

00:24:01.600 --> 00:24:03.378
fir un f- zaynen geven fun

00:24:03.378 --> 00:24:06.720
fir un fertsik, hob ikh zey gebrakht, biz finf un fertsik.

00:24:07.262 --> 00:24:08.870
a yor zaynen zey dortn geven,

00:24:08.870 --> 00:24:10.800
nokh, a yor, mer vi a yor.

00:24:10.800 --> 00:24:13.180
iz der bruder volt zey SNABZHAEn.

00:24:13.180 --> 00:24:18.740
der bruder, ikh, un ikh hob zeyer keyn tsayt nit gehat. ikh bin geven oyf der arbet zeyer farnumen

00:24:18.973 --> 00:24:25.580
mit, krign dem, di TOPLIVO mit, dos, di benzin mit, di ale zakhn far di fabrik,

00:24:25.580 --> 00:24:28.540
⟨iz dos⟩ geven sh- eyne fun di shverste zakhn.

00:24:28.626 --> 00:24:32.091
⟨TSISTERNes⟩, volt men darfn kumen un makhn ⟨TSISTERNes⟩.

00:24:32.091 --> 00:24:35.050
hot men gedarft, dortn hot men shoyn gedarft arbetn.

00:24:35.050 --> 00:24:38.678
volt ikh avekforn shabes, zuntik...

00:24:38.751 --> 00:24:42.620
neyn, zuntik bin ikh geven in der heym, avekforn m- zuntik far nakht,

00:24:42.620 --> 00:24:44.630
un kumen shabes krik.

00:24:44.691 --> 00:24:47.824
a vokh tsayt bin ikh nit geven in fabrik.

00:24:46.345 --> 00:24:48.460
nisht geven in shtub.

00:24:48.218 --> 00:24:49.607
kh'hob nit gehat keyn tsayt.

00:24:49.607 --> 00:24:52.510
un gelebt hob ikh shoyn, a dire hot men shoyn genumen.

00:24:52.510 --> 00:24:55.020
gelebt hob ikh in, in YAROSLAVL'.

00:24:55.086 --> 00:24:59.790
YAROSLA- YAROSLAVL', di shtot YAROSLAVL' hobn mir gelebt, gehat a dire,

00:24:59.790 --> 00:25:02.370
ikh mitn bruder, hobn mir shoyn gehat dortn a dire.

00:25:02.370 --> 00:25:05.910
di eltern hobn gelebt in BERENDEEVO, vu mir hobn gearbet,

00:25:05.910 --> 00:25:08.940
un mir voltn oysfirn, mit dem bruder oykh, volt avek⟨fo- ho⟩t eyn mol,

00:25:08.940 --> 00:25:12.354
m'hot gedarft brengen sp⟨e- s-⟩ zakhn far di arbeter...

00:25:12.354 --> 00:25:15.310
geven arbeter, vu mir hobn gearbet, geven zibn toyznt

00:25:15.310 --> 00:25:17.569
arbeter; s'iz geven a groyser farnem...

00:25:17.569 --> 00:25:19.840
iz er avekgeforn azh in Ural.

00:25:19.840 --> 00:25:23.540
iz er geven in Ural. UNK mir, di zakh ⟨iz⟩a zakh az mir hobn gehat

00:25:21.789 --> 00:25:23.100
UNK

00:25:23.540 --> 00:25:25.730
mit der velt tsu ton, ⟨hobn mir⟩ gehat.

00:25:25.730 --> 00:25:28.720
un dos hob ikh zikh oysgelernt dortn shoyn...

00:25:28.448 --> 00:25:32.256
un biz ven zent ir geven dort? biz finef un fertsik?

00:25:31.148 --> 00:25:35.361
ikh bin geven biz zeks, mir hot men a- mir hot men bafrayt

00:25:35.704 --> 00:25:37.503
in onheyb zeks un fertsik.

00:25:37.240 --> 00:25:39.390
onheyb zeks un fertsik.

00:25:38.740 --> 00:25:40.640
yo. zeks un fertsik.

00:25:40.075 --> 00:25:43.200
vos hey⟨s⟩t bafrayt? m'hot aykh bafrayt fun di arbet?

00:25:42.049 --> 00:25:47.940
⟨,⟩ ikh hob dokh geda- bafrayt fun der arbet, un dos iz shoyn ot vi fun di militer, ⟨volt men⟩ gebn medaln.

00:25:47.078 --> 00:25:48.078
⟨sh-⟩...

00:25:47.940 --> 00:25:49.740
alts iz gevezn vos s'iz

00:25:49.740 --> 00:25:51.172
punkt vi militer.

00:25:50.820 --> 00:25:54.159
UND ir hot gevust az di milkhome iz shoyn geendikt?

00:25:53.119 --> 00:25:57.480
endikt in fir un f- un fertsi- ikh hob gevust, ⟨n-⟩ ikh hob gehat radyo.

00:25:57.480 --> 00:25:59.370
dortn hob ikh shoyn gehat radyo.

00:25:59.370 --> 00:26:01.938
ikh hob gevust shoyn, m'hot bafrayt Dokshits.

00:26:01.911 --> 00:26:03.340
yo. yo, yo.

00:26:02.502 --> 00:26:06.610
ikh hob gevust, ikh hob gevust ven me bafrayt Dokshits un ikh hob shoyn

00:26:06.610 --> 00:26:12.300
gevust ven me bafrayt Vilne. ikh hob shoyn alts gevust.

00:26:11.935 --> 00:26:14.544
un ir hot gevust az se blaybt shoyn...

00:26:13.015 --> 00:26:18.460
az me hot bafrayt Dokshits, bin ikh gelegn un geveynt ot vi a kind.

00:26:18.718 --> 00:26:20.920
⟨,⟩ dos iz geven bay nakht.

00:26:21.148 --> 00:26:25.430
iz itster d⟨UNK⟩... un me hot bafrayt Vilne,

00:26:25.430 --> 00:26:27.009
iz shoyn der foter

00:26:27.009 --> 00:26:28.196
mit der

00:26:28.202 --> 00:26:30.508
mitlster shvester ASYA

00:26:30.666 --> 00:26:33.140
avekgeforn in Dokshits.

00:26:35.357 --> 00:26:37.130
ikh hob shoyn bakumen

00:26:37.130 --> 00:26:42.441
nokh der krig glaykh a briv fun UNK... ikh hob geshribn, gehat a farbindung mit Dokshits.

00:26:42.441 --> 00:26:44.050
hot men mir geentfert

00:26:44.050 --> 00:26:46.286
az yidn zaynen nit geblibn.

00:26:47.490 --> 00:26:50.940
ir hot geshribn un dos iz di tshuve vos ir hot genumen?

00:26:49.617 --> 00:26:52.920
ikh hob geshribn un gefregt, vos makht d-, vos tut zikh dortn?

00:26:52.920 --> 00:26:54.302
hot men mir geshribn.

00:26:54.308 --> 00:26:58.200
bin ikh avekgeforn in gest... nokh nit bafrayt geven...

00:26:58.200 --> 00:27:02.368
a kuk ton, ⟨bin ikh⟩ gekumen ahin, ⟨hob ikh gezen,⟩ gekumen ahin UNK glaykh gefaln.

00:27:02.391 --> 00:27:04.640
a kuk geton vos s'tut zikh...

00:27:03.489 --> 00:27:05.150
vos hot ir gezen?

00:27:04.640 --> 00:27:08.930
ikh hob gezen di griber vu m'iz geven farshotn. der foter

00:27:08.930 --> 00:27:14.200
hot geven, ⟨zey hobn⟩, epes a komisye iz gekumen ⟨un hobn⟩ gekukt, UNK gegrobn. der foter iz dortn geven.

00:27:14.200 --> 00:27:15.997
ikh bin nit geven, nor der foter.

00:27:15.997 --> 00:27:20.308
un m'hot gezen az di mentshn vos m'hot geharget un bashotn,

00:27:20.308 --> 00:27:22.770
geven farshotn mit kalkh.

00:27:23.569 --> 00:27:29.310
az m'hot bakumen fun dortn beyner, iz geven ot vi porekh, oyfgegesene.

00:27:29.310 --> 00:27:32.160
volt men nor nemen in hant, volt dos tseshitn zikh.

00:27:33.694 --> 00:27:36.670
zey hobn geshosn dortn in Dokshits?

00:27:35.230 --> 00:27:43.290
zey hobn dortn, in Dokshits iz geven griber lebn dem besalmen. dos iz geven take nit vayt vu mir hobn gelebt ⟨a, in,⟩ azoy on a zayt. UNK...

00:27:41.676 --> 00:27:45.703
ir hot gelebt, ir hot gelebt noent tsum vald?

00:27:44.865 --> 00:27:47.132
ikh hob gelebt noent,

00:27:47.132 --> 00:27:51.660
noent nit tsum tsenter, oder noent tsum, tsum breg.

00:27:51.660 --> 00:27:55.930
dortn iz geven azetike griber bay undz; zamd volt men nemen dortn, alts.

00:27:55.930 --> 00:27:59.050
un dortn hot men gefirt di yidn un m'hot dortn ale geshosn,

00:27:59.050 --> 00:28:01.690
afile di vos zaynen geven in JUDENRAT!

00:27:59.057 --> 00:28:00.057
⟨v-⟩....

00:28:01.909 --> 00:28:05.078
s'zaynen geven dokh yidn in JUDENRAT un yidishe mil-

00:28:05.078 --> 00:28:07.829
di politseyske yidishe UNK ⟨hobn⟩ zey gemakht.

00:28:07.829 --> 00:28:12.420
m'hot ale oysgeshosn. s'iz, zey hot men di letste, nor zey hobn gedarft nokh

00:28:09.211 --> 00:28:10.211
⟨v-⟩...

00:28:12.420 --> 00:28:15.350
kukn vi men shist di, un nakher hot UNK...

00:28:15.350 --> 00:28:18.545
mir hob- ikh bin gekumen, hob ikh gefunen partizaner.

00:28:18.545 --> 00:28:20.789
eyner mayner a khaver iz geven,

00:28:20.789 --> 00:28:25.055
di vos zaynen nokh nit antlofn. er iz geven in vald di gantse tsayt,

00:28:25.062 --> 00:28:26.710
ir hot ge- ir hot g-

00:28:25.062 --> 00:28:29.612
Yos- Yos⟨ik⟩. mir hobn, mir, ikh hob mit im dortn zikh getrofn. ⟨hot er...⟩

00:28:28.470 --> 00:28:33.260
ir hot getrofn partizanen vos zenen geven, vos zenen geblibn in vald,

00:28:32.115 --> 00:28:33.850
geblibn in vald.

00:28:33.260 --> 00:28:37.222
zenen nisht vayter gelofn in Rusland arayn azoy vi enk?

00:28:35.895 --> 00:28:39.080
neyn, zey zaynen geblibn in der heym, zaynen zey geblibn,

00:28:39.080 --> 00:28:41.154
un zey zaynen shoyn fun geto gelofn.

00:28:41.785 --> 00:28:43.500
ot dem khaver vos...

00:28:41.818 --> 00:28:46.460
a! zey zenen antlofn in vald arayn ven m'hot gemakht a geto.

00:28:45.852 --> 00:28:50.300
ven m'hot gemakht a geto zaynen zey gelofn in vald. der vald iz shoyn geven organizirt.

00:28:50.300 --> 00:28:51.752
ikh bin nit geven ⟨dor-...⟩

00:28:50.920 --> 00:28:55.413
ven ets zents geven in vald iz nokh nisht geven organizirt partizanen.

00:28:54.306 --> 00:28:58.520
ven ikh bin geven iz nokh gorn- zog ikh aykh, ven ikh bin gelofn

00:28:58.520 --> 00:29:01.652
iz in TSAVA nit geven organizirt; s'iz geven

00:29:01.652 --> 00:29:02.856
a tuml.

00:29:02.963 --> 00:29:07.277
der hot gebombirt, dem geharget, dem mit a... m'hot nit gevust eyner fun tsveytn.

00:29:07.519 --> 00:29:09.610
ikh hob nokh partizaner nit...

00:29:09.610 --> 00:29:12.997
az s'iz, vos zay- ikh b- hert, ot do iz nokh do, az ikh bin...

00:29:11.670 --> 00:29:16.625
undz vel'mir vay- ir vet, ir vet mir vayter dertseyln oyf di nekste kasete, OKAY?

00:29:16.294 --> 00:29:20.530
BESEDER. a, a, s'iz shoyn geendikt di kasete. ⟨BESEDER⟩.

00:29:16.918 --> 00:29:17.995
BESEDER.
